---

<section class="py-24 bg-background-dark relative">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 tech-grid opacity-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span
        class="text-primary font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-3 block"
        >Cualificación</span
      >
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white font-display">
        ¿Es este servicio para vos?
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16">
      <div
        class="bg-surface-dark border border-border-dark p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-sm relative"
      >
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-green-500"></div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center">
          <svg
            class="w-7 h-7 text-green-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="currentColor"
            aria-hidden="true"
            ><path
              d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"
            ></path></svg
          >
          Es para vos si:
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg
              class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
              ><path
                d="M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z"
              ></path></svg
            >
            <span class="text-text-dim text-sm"
              >Sos un Coach o Consultor invirtiendo en tráfico pago y necesitas
              maximizar el ROI.</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg
              class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
              ><path
                d="M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z"
              ></path></svg
            >
            <span class="text-text-dim text-sm"
              >Gestionas un Ecommerce con ventas constantes que busca mejorar la
              tasa de conversión.</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg
              class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
              ><path
                d="M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z"
              ></path></svg
            >
            <span class="text-text-dim text-sm"
              >Tenés una Marca Personal en escalado y tu web actual ya no te
              representa.</span
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div
        class="bg-surface-dark border border-border-dark p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-sm relative opacity-80"
      >
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-red-500"></div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center">
          <svg
            class="w-7 h-7 text-red-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="currentColor"
            aria-hidden="true"
            ><path
              d="M12 2C6.47 2 2 6.47 2 12s4.47 10 10 10 10-4.47 10-10S17.53 2 12 2zm5 13.59L15.59 17 12 13.41 8.41 17 7 15.59 10.59 12 7 8.41 8.41 7 12 10.59 15.59 7 17 8.41 13.41 12 17 15.59z"
            ></path></svg
          >
          No es para vos si:
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg
              class="w-4 h-4 text-red-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
              ><path
                d="M19 6.41L17.59 5 12 10.59 6.41 5 5 6.41 10.59 12 5 17.59 6.41 19 12 13.41 17.59 19 19 17.59 13.41 12z"
              ></path></svg
            >
            <span class="text-text-dim text-sm"
              >Buscas la opción más barata del mercado (priorizamos calidad y
              retorno).</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg
              class="w-4 h-4 text-red-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
              ><path
                d="M19 6.41L17.59 5 12 10.59 6.41 5 5 6.41 10.59 12 5 17.59 6.41 19 12 13.41 17.59 19 19 17.59 13.41 12z"
              ></path></svg
            >
            <span class="text-text-dim text-sm"
              >Necesitas una web "para ayer" (nuestro proceso estratégico toma
              2-3 semanas).</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg
              class="w-4 h-4 text-red-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="currentColor"
              aria-hidden="true"
              ><path
                d="M19 6.41L17.59 5 12 10.59 6.41 5 5 6.41 10.59 12 5 17.59 6.41 19 12 13.41 17.59 19 19 17.59 13.41 12z"
              ></path></svg
            >
            <span class="text-text-dim text-sm"
              >No tienes una oferta validada ni sabes quién es tu cliente ideal.</span
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
